[ :arr |
  arr size => [n |
    0 to: n - 2 do: [i |
      i => [minIdx |
        i + 1 to: n - 1 do: [j |
          (arr at: j) < (arr at: minIdx) 
            ifTrue: [j => minIdx]
        ].
        (arr at: i) => [tmp |
          arr at: i put: (arr at: minIdx).
          arr at: minIdx put: tmp
        ]
      ]
    ]
  ].
  arr
] => selectionSort.

{5. 2. 8. 1. 9. 3} selectionSort printLine.